<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ title }} · 과학 한 모금</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ deck or siteDescription }}">
<link rel="icon" href="/assets/favicon.svg">
<link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="과학 한 모금 RSS" href="/feed.xml">
{% include "seo.njk" %}
{% include "_style.njk" %}
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-head">
  <a class="brand" href="/">☕ 과학 한 모금</a>
</header>
{% include "_nav.njk" %}

<main class="article-grid">
  <div class="article-head">
    <span class="cat">{{ category }}</span>
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="deck">{{ deck }}</p>
    <div class="head-meta">
      <time>{{ displayDate }}</time>
      {% if source %}<a class="source-link" href="{{ source }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📄 원문 보기 →</a>{% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="article-body">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>
  {% if "/deepdive/" not in page.url and "/preview/" not in page.url %}<p class="byline-sign">☕ 과저씨가 한 모금으로 풀어드렸어요</p>{% endif %}
</main>

<footer class="site-foot">
  <a href="/">← 전체 기사</a>
  <a class="feedback-link" href="mailto:ohyuk1220@naver.com?subject=과학 한 모금 의견·불편한 점">💬 불편한 점·의견 보내기</a>
  <span>과학 한 모금 · 전시실 뒷방</span>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
